channel.title: DominationX || 317 || Godwars || Chaotics || Dragon Claws
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/DominationX.jpg[/img]
With a plan of making a good server I decided to stop with delta servers, due to the low amount of features that delta based servers offer, so I started with PI. In the beginning it was a little hard, but later I got used to it, and this is the result. It will be public once I have found a host.
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/features.png[/img]Barrows[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/features.png[/img] - Killing for killcount - Open the chest when all brothers are dead
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Clue_scroll.gif[/img]Treasure trails[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Clue_scroll.gif[/img] - Opening at any spot - Fabulous rewards - Dropped by only the best monsters
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Bandos-godsword-inv.png[/img]GodWars[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Bandos-godsword-inv.png[/img] - 20 Killcount to fight any boss - All 4 bosses with perfect animations - God-armour and godsword shards
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/m97reh.gif[/img]Duel Arena[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/m97reh.gif[/img] - Working target with arrow gfx - Perfect rules selecting - Staking available - Working forfeiting
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/dungeon_chaotic_maul.gif[/img]Chaotics[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/dungeon_chaotic_maul.gif[/img] - All 3 the melee weapons - Only available by donating - Working animations
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/CombatSwords.png[/img]Combat[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/CombatSwords.png[/img] - Perfect special attacks - Realistic hitting - Perfect running in - Poison with Anti-Poison Potion
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Magic-icon.png[/img]Magic[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Magic-icon.png[/img] - Perfect hybriding - Perfect vengeance - Player and NPC freezing works - Perfect Teleblock - Fully working telekinetic grab - Perfect delays
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Ranged-icon.png[/img]Ranged[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Ranged-icon.png[/img] - Perfect dark bow special - Perfect switching - Dragon arrows - Bolts with perfect effects
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Prayer-icon.png[/img]Prayer[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Prayer-icon.png[/img] - All prayers, including turmoil - Prayer-on-Altar works - Correct stat bonuses
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Crafting-icon.png[/img]Crafting[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Crafting-icon.png[/img] - Ranged armor crafting - Uncuts crafting
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Herblore-icon.png[/img]Herblore[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Herblore-icon.png[/img] - All potions and herbs available - Clean herbs (EG. Clean guam) - XP rate based on farming
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Farming-icon.png[/img]Farming[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Farming-icon.png[/img] - Custom seeds-on-patch method - All herbs compitable with the patch
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Fletching-icon.png[/img]Fletching[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Fletching-icon.png[/img] - Bolt crafting (Including diamond/dragon and onyx) - Arrow crafting (Including dragon arrows) - Bow crafting
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Thieving-icon.png[/img]Thieving[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Thieving-icon.png[/img] - Stalls which give money from 5-15K - NPC pickpocketing
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Woodcutting-icon.png[/img]Woodcutting[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Woodcutting-icon.png[/img] - All trees working - Axe required - Realistic XP rate
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Fishing-icon.png[/img]Fishing[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Fishing-icon.png[/img] - Fishing delays - Level requirements
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Cooking-icon.png[/img]Cooking[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Cooking-icon.png[/img] - Fish cooking - No more burning
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Mining-icon.png[/img]Mining[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Mining-icon.png[/img] - All ores - Mining zone - Delays and level requirements
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Smithing-icon.png[/img]Smithing[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Smithing-icon.png[/img] - All bars available - Dragonfire-shield smithing
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Agility-icon.png[/img]Agility[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Agility-icon.png[/img] - Wilderniss course - Gnome agility course
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Runecrafting-icon.png[/img]Runecrafting[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Runecrafting-icon.png[/img] - All runecrafting altars - Talk to zamorak mage to go altars
[IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Cbowspecs.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Chaotics.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Clanchat.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Dbowspec.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Dclawsspec.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Lunars.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Prayers.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/PvPitems.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h393/Stijn12345/Whips.jpg[/img]
That's about everything i have to offer you. Please comment nice, because this is my first public development.

item.description:
@Rickrolla wrote:

DominationX.jpg800×600

With a plan of making a good server I decided to stop with delta servers, due to the low amount of features that delta based servers offer, so I started with PI.
In the beginning it was a little hard, but later I got used to it, and this is the result.
It will be public once I have found a host.

Barrows

  • Killing for killcount
  • Open the chest when all brothers are dead

Treasure trails

  • Opening at any spot
  • Fabulous rewards
  • Dropped by only the best monsters

GodWars

  • 20 Killcount to fight any boss
  • All 4 bosses with perfect animations
  • God-armour and godsword shards

Duel Arena

  • Working target with arrow gfx
  • Perfect rules selecting
  • Staking available
  • Working forfeiting

Chaotics

  • All 3 the melee weapons
  • Only available by donating
  • Working animations

Combat

  • Perfect special attacks
  • Realistic hitting
  • Perfect running in
  • Poison with Anti-Poison Potion

Magic

  • Perfect hybriding
  • Perfect vengeance
  • Player and NPC freezing works
  • Perfect Teleblock
  • Fully working telekinetic grab
  • Perfect delays

Ranged

  • Perfect dark bow special
  • Perfect switching
  • Dragon arrows
  • Bolts with perfect effects

Prayer

  • All prayers, including turmoil
  • Prayer-on-Altar works
  • Correct stat bonuses

Crafting

  • Ranged armor crafting
  • Uncuts crafting

Herblore

  • All potions and herbs available
  • Clean herbs (EG. Clean guam)
  • XP rate based on farming

Farming

  • Custom seeds-on-patch method
  • All herbs compitable with the patch

Fletching

  • Bolt crafting (Including diamond/dragon and onyx)
  • Arrow crafting (Including dragon arrows)
  • Bow crafting

Thieving

  • Stalls which give money from 5-15K
  • NPC pickpocketing

Woodcutting

  • All trees working
  • Axe required
  • Realistic XP rate

Fishing

  • Fishing delays
  • Level requirements

Cooking

  • Fish cooking
  • No more burning

Mining

  • All ores
  • Mining zone
  • Delays and level requirements

Smithing

  • All bars available
  • Dragonfire-shield smithing

Agility

  • Wilderniss course
  • Gnome agility course

Runecrafting

  • All runecrafting altars
  • Talk to zamorak mage to go altars






Lunars.jpg760×504



That’s about everything i have to offer you.
Please comment nice, because this is my first public development.
